page.title: 16SUPERNATURAL
page.content: WE INVESTIGATED SUPERNATURAL ACTIVITIES IN NORTHFIELD.WE LOOKED AT BELIEF IN GHOSTS,STRANGE HAPPENINGS,DREAMS AND SUPERSTITIONS.A SMALL SURVEY WAS CARRIED OUT.WE ASKED 71 PEOPLE IF THEY HAVE HAD A DREAM COME TRUE.9 SAID YES, 62 SAID NO.THESE ARE SOME OF THEIR DREAMS-MEETING A HUSBAND,WINNING THE POOLS,OUT OF 73 PEOPLE 4 HAD A GHOST TO DO WITH THEIR FAMILY.WE ASKED 73 PEOPLE IF THEY HAVE HAD A STRANGE HAPPENING.12 SAID YES AND 61 SAID NO. THERE ARE 2 OF THEM WHO HAD A PICTURE FALL OFF A WALL.
